channel.description: Workforce Identity Cloud (WIC) overview Click here to give feedback about this page Content Notes Target personas: New IAM Developers,Developers new to Okta Description: Explains WIC and compares it to the CIC domain. Describes the domain of what developer.okta.com covers. Why is this here?: - 26% of respondents could not identify Workforce Identity Cloud despite “Workforce” being in the definition. Developers new to IAM and Okta are less satisfied with the docs and visit rarely.
